snippet.title: Grimoire Groves - Official Gameplay Trailer | Wholesome Direct 2023
snippet.description:
Explore the colorful world of Grimoire Groves and learn more about this upcoming rogue-lite dungeon crawler game where you grow plants with magic, befriend magical creatures, and more. A Kickstarter campaign for Grimoire Groves is available now.

#SummerOfGaming
